metadata.name: Purification
metadata.description:
Versions of who I once thought I was line up to be tested in truth.  
And anything that is not true is destroyed,  
With the hope that one dayâ€¦  
The version of who I believe myself to be 
Will fully embody who I truly am. 
On that day, the fire will cease, 
And the process of purification will be complete.
